Package gov.sandia.geotess

Class GeoTessPositionLinear

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.sandia.geotess.GeoTessPosition
      • gov.sandia.geotess.GeoTessPositionLinear
  • public class GeoTessPositionLinear
extends GeoTessPosition
    Perform linear interpolation for an arbitrary point in the 3D model. First visits every profile at a vertex of current triangle and finds linear, radial, interpolation coefficients at radial nodes. Then uses the 6 coefficients to compute interpolated values.

    There is no public constructor. Call GeoTessModel.getPosition(InterpolatorType.LINEAR) to obtain an instance.
